1
00:00:14,840 --> 00:00:16,000
Who are you here for?

2
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:17,760
I'm here to see Tawan.

3
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:19,280
Is this her house?

4
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:21,880
Ms. Tawan doesn't live here anymore.

5
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:25,200
Then...

6
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,200
do you have her contact number?

7
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:31,880
I don't. I'm really sorry.

8
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:55,560
♪ I want you to know my heart for once ♪

9
00:00:55,560 --> 00:01:01,480
♪ My gaze is me hoping for you to listen ♪

10
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:06,240
♪ To what my heart feels about you ♪

11
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:10,640
♪ But you never pay me any mind ♪

12
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:14,320
♪ No matter how much I try ♪

13
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:20,280
♪ You close your heart and keep ignoring me ♪

14
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:24,320
♪ The closer we are, the further it feels ♪

15
00:01:24,320 --> 00:01:27,720
♪ Never once ♪

16
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:32,680
♪ Did you notice what my heart was feeling ♪

17
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,680
Now that you're by yourself,

18
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,040
the rain won't stop.

19
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,480
♪ When I look at you, my eyes say it all ♪

20
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,400
♪ Waiting only for you to pay me attention ♪

21
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,560
It's best you come home with me.

22
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:50,560
♪ My heart yells every day
But its voice never reaches you ♪

23
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:54,560
♪ I want you to know how long I've kept this in ♪

24
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:59,200
♪ Do you have any idea ♪

25
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,880
♪ As each minute goes by ♪

26
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:07,640
♪ How much my heart wants to say I love you? ♪

27
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:12,560
♪ All I know is my heart's stubborn ♪

28
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:16,560
♪ Even when you ignore me
There's pain but also love ♪

29
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:20,760
♪ That has never lessened ♪

30
