But its voice never reaches you ♪

37
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,600
Can you promise me that

38
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:56,320
from this day on, no matter what happens,

39
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,680
you won't forget who you are?

40
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,880
Keep up your grades.

41
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,320
Follow your dreams.

42
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:08,000
I believe that your perseverance

43
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:11,080
will lead you down a good path.

44
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,480
Stay strong.

45
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:20,640
I'll always be rooting for you.

46
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:44,080
I promise you I will do my best.

47
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,200
I will realize my dreams.

48
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,760
Spotlights will shine on me.

49
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:53,920
And when I'm successful enough,

50
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:57,920
when every pair of eyes are fixed on me,

51
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:04,840
you will see me then,

52
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:08,200
and I will get you back.

53
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,920
Failed!

54
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,360
Go back to training.

55
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,040
I no longer trust your company.

56
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,640
I'll find my daughter's bodyguard myself.

57
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:41,920
As far as I know,
I don't meet your criteria at all.

58
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,680
I don't think we need to
look for another company, Dad.

59
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:46,880
Looking forward to working with you,

60
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,680
Ms. Bodyguard.

61
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,600
